
 sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant InputHandler
    participant VideoDownloader
    participant VideoConverter
    participant Uploader
    participant Logger

    User->>InputHandler: Provide YouTube URL
    InputHandler->>Logger: Log input
    InputHandler->>VideoDownloader: Pass validated URL
    VideoDownloader->>Logger: Log download start
    VideoDownloader->>VideoConverter: Pass raw video
    VideoConverter->>Logger: Log conversion
    VideoConverter->>Uploader: Pass MP4 video
    Uploader->>Logger: Log upload status 
